1. LAION CLAP (clap-htsat-unfused) — the encoder weights

The audio and text encoders clapkit runs are CoreML conversions of LAION's
`clap-htsat-unfused`. clapkit ships NO model files; it loads FinDIT-Studio's
conversion (below), which is a derivative work of the LAION weights. CC-BY-4.0
requires attribution when redistributing the weights (or a binary bundling
them).

